replies.body:
Mmm, I like the concept but the problem is that I (and lots of other players I know) change their flash key depending on which lane they're playing. 

For instance when I play top lane I arrange my summoner spells like this:{{summoner:4}} {{summoner:12}} 
However when I play mid lane I arrange my summoner spells like this:{{summoner:14}} {{summoner:4}}

So I feel like the system would also have to balance in notable differences in KDA along with summoner spell swaps.
